headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Tesla Shares Skid as Trump and Musk Tussle Over Budget Bill
summary: The S&P 500 fell 0.6% on Thursday, June 5, as unemployment claims raised doubts about the labor market ahead of Friday morning's jobs report.
